OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAfter a bright start, cloud
OL,6,Fbecoming more widespread through the
OL,7,Fmorning with showery outbreaks of rain
OL,8,Fin the west. Isolated thunderstorms
OL,9,Fpossible later in the day. Feeling
OL,10,Fvery warm and humid.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers easing this evening
OL,13,Fto leave a dry night with clear skies.
OL,14,FAnother mild night to come with light
OL,15,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
