OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FAnother bright start with
OL,6,Fcloud increasing through the day.
OL,7,FShowery rain possible in the west
OL,8,Fbefore becoming more persistent and
OL,9,Fheavier into the evening. Still warm
OL,10,Fand humid.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FShowers
OL,13,For longer spells of rain likely
OL,14,Fthrough Sunday and into Monday,
OL,15,Fpossibly thundery. A few showers still
OL,16,Fpossible Tuesday. Feeling cooler early
OL,17,Fnext week.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
